Detailed Description

finds arbitrary template in the grayscale image using Generalized Hough Transform Ballard, D.H. (1981). Generalizing the Hough transform to detect arbitrary shapes. Pattern Recognition 13 (2): 111-122. Guil, N., Gonz√°lez-Linares, J.M. and Zapata, E.L. (1999). Bidimensional shape detection using an invariant approach. Pattern Recognition 32 (6): 1025-1038.
